  <h1>FOUNDERS' / SHAREHOLDERS' AGREEMENT</h1>
  <p style="text-align:center;"><strong>{{company_name}}</strong><br>
  Effective Date: {{effective_date}}</p>
  <hr>

  <p>This Founders' / Shareholders' Agreement (the "Agreement") is entered into on {{effective_date}} by and among the undersigned founders and shareholders of <strong>{{company_name}}</strong>, a {{state_of_incorporation}} corporation (the "Company").</p>

  <h2>1. Purpose</h2>
  <p>This Agreement sets forth the mutual understanding of the Founders regarding their rights, obligations, and ownership interests in the Company, as well as the management and operation of the Company and protection of its intellectual property.</p>

  <h2>2. Parties</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Title/Role</th>
        <th>Equity %</th>
        <th>Shares</th>
        <th>Vesting</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
